  <brief_title>Muscle-in-vein Conduits for Digital Nerve Reconstruction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Sensory Recovery After Reconstruction of Digital Nerves of the Hand Using Muscle-in-vein Conduits in Comparison to Nerve Suture or Nerve Transplantation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
