  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The actual study should provide a first direct comparison between results after
      reconstruction of sensory nerves of the hand using muscle-in-vein conduits to the standard
      methods of nerve transplantation and direct nerve suture.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
